	* [r11589] What LCAO alternative calls this%nbasis is the same as
	  what the standard LCAO calls this%norbs.

2013-12-16 17:48  acastro

	* [r11590] No reason why one cannot move the ions when using the
	  Crank-Nicolson
	  propagation scheme.

