2015-02-19 17:39  xavier

	* [r13115] src/scf/lcao.F90: Backport of 13083 to branches/5.0.x:
	  ------------------------------------------------------------------------
	  r13083 | xavier | 2015-02-18 09:06:35 -0800 (Wed, 18 Feb 2015) |
	  3 lines
	  
