2015-03-24 16:53  dstrubbe

	* [r13524] src/hamiltonian/born_charges.F90,
	  src/hamiltonian/scf_tol.F90, src/main/casida.F90,
	  src/sternheimer/em_resp.F90, src/system/linear_solver.F90,
