	* [r13526] m4/pfft.m4: Backport of 13503 to branches/5.0.x:
	  ------------------------------------------------------------------------
	  r13503 | dstrubbe | 2015-03-23 20:52:25 -0400 (Mon, 23 Mar 2015)
	  | 2 lines
	  
